6. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect any data collected. However, since TheAIBook.info is an informational directory, no sensitive personal data is stored.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy occasionally. Revised versions will be posted here.

8. Contact Us
If you have any privacy-related concerns, reach out via our Contact Page.

